OL,3,CBakery manager settles age
OL,4,Cdiscrimination case for #75k
OL,6,FA 60-year-old man has settled an age
OL,7,Fdiscrimination case against his former
OL,8,Femployer, Irwin's bakery, for #75,000.
OL,10,FSeamus Gillespie, who was a sales
OL,11,Fmanager, alleged he was told the
OL,12,Fcompany was looking for younger
OL,13,Fprofessional people as part of a
OL,14,Frecruitment drive.
OL,16,FThe case was supported by the Equality
OL,17,FCommission for Northern Ireland and
OL,18,Fwas settled without admission of
OL,19,Fliability by the company.
