OL,3,CBakery manager settles age
OL,4,Cdiscrimination case for #75k
OL,6,F"I envisaged I would finish my working
OL,7,Fcareer in Irwin's bakery," Mr
OL,8,FGillespie told UTV.
OL,10,F"I love my job I loved what I was
OL,11,Fdoing I believed I was very good at it
OL,12,Fand I was so disappointed with the way
OL,13,Fit ended."
OL,15,FMr Gillespie, from Co Fermanagh,
OL,16,Fworked for the bakery since 1991.
