OL,6,FHe alleged that he was told in early
OL,7,F2021 that the company was looking for
OL,8,Fyounger professional people from a
OL,9,Fblue-chip background in the context of
OL,10,Frecruitment for new staff.
OL,12,FHe believes this was because the
OL,13,Fcompany thought the age profile of
OL,14,Fstaff within the business was a
OL,15,Fproblem.
OL,17,FMr Gillespie also alleged that he was
OL,18,Finformed that he would lose some
OL,19,Faccounts when a vacant post of
OL,20,F'Business Unit Controller' was to be
OL,21,Ffilled.
