OL,6,FHe believed that this resulted in him
OL,7,Flosing a significant proportion of his
OL,8,Fwork. He felt his role was diminished
OL,9,Fand that he was left in a vulnerable
OL,10,Fposition for possible future
OL,11,Fredundancy.
OL,13,FIn August 2022, Mr Gillespie was
OL,14,Finformed of a project involving
OL,15,Fchanges in distribution. He believed
OL,16,Fthat he should have been included in
OL,17,Fthe relevant discussions because it
OL,18,Fimpacted upon his work.
