OL,6,FMr Gillespie said: "I worked for
OL,7,FIrwins for over 30 years. I enjoyed my
OL,8,Fjob, I was a dedicated, hardworking
OL,9,Fand loyal employee, with lots of
OL,10,Fexperience.
OL,12,F"But it was very clear to me,
OL,13,Ffollowing discussions with management,
OL,14,Fthat my career with the company was
OL,15,Fover.
