OL,4,Cdiscrimination case for #75k
OL,6,F"I firmly believed the decision to
OL,7,Fmake me redundant was based solely on
OL,8,Fmy age. I had no choice but to
OL,9,Fchallenge how I was treated. I'm glad
OL,10,Fmy case is now settled, although I
OL,11,Fwould rather that none of this had
OL,12,Fhappened in the first place."
OL,14,FGeraldine McGahey, Chief Commissioner,
OL,15,FEquality Commission for Northern
OL,16,FIreland said: "Seamus gave 30 years of
OL,17,Fhis working life to Irwin's Bakery and
OL,18,Fstill had a lot to offer. He felt that
OL,19,Fhis age was a problem for his employer
OL,20,Fand believes that was why he was made
OL,21,Fredundant.
