OL,3,CBakery manager settles age
OL,4,Cdiscrimination case for #75k
OL,6,F"In Northern Ireland it is unlawful to
OL,7,Fdiscriminate against employees because
OL,8,Fof their age.
OL,10,F"Older workers have experience, skills
OL,11,Fand attributes that our economy needs
OL,12,Fto thrive, they are assets to their
OL,13,Femployers just like every other
OL,14,Femployee.
OL,16,F"It is imperative that employers have
OL,17,Frobust policies and practices in place
OL,18,Fto prevent any potential instances of
OL,19,Fage discrimination and that staff are
OL,20,Fadequately trained to use them,"
OL,21,Fconcluded Ms McGahey.
