OL,6,FIn setting the case, WD Irwin and Sons
OL,7,FLtd denied any liability and
OL,8,Freaffirmed its strong commitment to
OL,9,Fthe principle of equality of
OL,10,Fopportunity in employment and to
OL,11,Fensuring that they comply in all
OL,12,Frespects with their obligations under
OL,13,Fequality law.
OL,15,FThey agreed to liaise with the
OL,16,FEquality Commission to review
OL,17,Fpolicies, practices and procedures and
OL,18,Ftheir application to ensure that they
OL,19,Fare effective and conform with the
OL,20,Frequirements of the Employment
OL,21,FEquality Age Regulations (NI) 2006.
